Game Description:
******************
You have been hired as a private investigator to search for the missing heir to the old estate in Scotland. It would be expected that everyone in an abandoned house should sleep soundly and strong. But that assumption is wrong ...The house has a life hidden from the eyes of the novice. Within its walls have long inhabited by the spirits and ghosts. And only IF you play by their rules, will they let you into their dominion.

Game Features:
***************
Are you ready to explore all the secrets of a spooky abandoned house to find the missing heir?

